# Calculating Pi with Amazon Lambdas

Parallelizing a task with Amazon Lambdas can be a lot of fun. This will be a lightning short introduction to using Amazon Lambdas and how to call them while calculating Pi.

### Points to cover
- Creating an Amazone Lambda function
- Creating the HTTP request trigger
- Connecting the two
- Running the sample Pi calculator app
- Looking at the monitoring graphs available in Amazon's Lambda service
